# Client Boundary & UI

## Do not import on client

- `lib/prisma.ts`, `repositories/*`, `services/*` that use Prisma
- `@/app/generated/prisma/client`
- Server-only: `authorizeAction`, `requireRole`, `createAdminClient`

Pass **DTOs** as props from server pages. For labels/enums use `constants/*` (e.g. `constants/expenses.ts`, `constants/reports.ts`).

## UI patterns

- shadcn Button: use `buttonVariants` + `Link` instead of `asChild`
- Forms: `FormData` + `useTransition` + `toast` + `router.refresh()` (see `customer-manager.tsx`)
- Lists: `SearchInput`, `PaginationControls`, `EmptyState`, `DeleteConfirmDialog`
- Currency/dates: `formatCurrency`, `formatDate`, `formatDateTime` from `lib/format`
- Page shell: `mx-auto max-w-7xl space-y-6` + title + muted description

## Zustand

Only for ephemeral UI (POS cart in `stores/pos.store.ts`). Server state via server pages + `router.refresh()`, not duplicated in Query for CRUD lists.
